        {
            "+content": "Clouds blacken the sky and sheets of rain turn the mountain forest into a treacherous maze... A landslide crushes a razor wire fence and buries a \"NO TRESPASSING\" sign... Two young siblings wander into a dark world where they do not belong, and a long, horrid shadow rears up to meet them. Anyway, so that's how we met Dara-san. She might look kinda scary, but just wait until you get to know her. <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
